{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"eunomia-bpf","page":{"layout":"document","title":"benchmark","description":"Most of the time, bpf-loader work as a library to load eBPF program. It will not affect eBPF program after the program has been loaded and attached.","descriptionIsExcerpt":true,"bodyHtml":"<p>Most of the time, bpf-loader work as a library to load eBPF program. It will not affect eBPF program after the program has been loaded and attached.</p>\n<p>TODO: add more benchmark results</p>\n<h2 id=\"benchmark-for-loading-with-exporter\">benchmark for loading with exporter</h2>\n<p>Take opensnoop from <a href=\"https://github.com/iovisor/bcc/blob/master/libbpf-tools/opensnoop.bpf.c\">bcc/libbpf-tools</a> as an example. starting with BCC, you will need about 0.8s to start the exporter and attach to the probe. With out implement, you only need about <code>50-70ms</code> which is significantly faster.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"shellsession\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"shellsession\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">$ ps -aux </span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">|</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> grep</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> eunomia</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">root      171562  0.0  0.0  15176  4576 pts/6    S+   01:08   0:00 sudo ./eunomia-exporter</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">root      171605  0.1  0.0 350540  7740 pts/6    Sl+  01:08   0:00 ./eunomia-exporter</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>The memory usage and CPU usage is also low. see <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/tree/master/eunomia-sdks/eunomia-otel\">eunomia-exporter</a> for more details.</p>","tags":[],"headings":[{"id":"benchmark-for-loading-with-exporter","text":"benchmark for loading with exporter","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/benchmark.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2024-01-26T22:09:57.000Z","createdAt":"2023-08-10T12:54:12.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"},{"name":"oluceps","email":"ospp@oluceps.uk"}]},"path":"/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","description":"Simplify eBPF development with CO-RE and WebAssembly. Build, compile, and distribute eBPF programs easier with automatic code generation.","href":"/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"Project architecture","description":"we have a loader library, a compile toolchain, and some additional tools like cli and a custom metrics exporter.","href":"/eunomia-bpf/architecture/"},"next":{"title":"ecc docker usage","description":"``shell yourprogram.bpf.c yourprogram.h optional, if you want to use ring buffer to export events ``","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf Documentation","href":"/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","depth":1},{"title":"ecli server","href":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","depth":2},{"title":"exporter","href":"/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","depth":1},{"title":"usage","href":"/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"introduction","href":"/eunomia-bpf/introduction/","depth":1},{"title":"manual","href":"/eunomia-bpf/manual/","depth":1},{"title":"Online Demo","href":"/eunomia-bpf/online/","depth":1},{"title":"quickstart","href":"/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","depth":1},{"title":"build on android aarch64","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","depth":2},{"title":"build from source","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","depth":2},{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","href":"/eunomia-bpf/setup/","depth":1},{"title":"supporting-external-BTF","href":"/eunomia-bpf/supporting-external-BTF/","depth":1},{"title":"video","href":"/eunomia-bpf/video/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}